    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-03-09T11:29:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-03-09T11:29:00-05:00" n="798"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d798">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 837.711/18</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Cuba</hi> (<persName
                        corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_GWE1" type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gonzales</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-03-09T11:00:00-05:29">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 9, 1918, 11 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received 11.45 a.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mine, March 6, 12 a.m.<note n="1" xml:id="d798fn1">Not printed.</note> Two
                    steamships from Spain being due today, one bound for Mexico, I urged upon
                    President that pending general action upon censorship this mail for Mexico be
                    examined. He has just replied: “I took up matter with Spanish Minister and it
                    has been settled in accordance with your wishes.”</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_GWE1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Gonzales</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
